cli

ros2 topic list -t 
ros2 topic echo --count 3 /turtle1/cmd_vel
ros2 topic info /turtle1/cmd_vel
ros2 topic hz /turtle1/cmd_vel

ros2 interface show geometry_msgs/msgs/Twist
ros2 interface prot geometry_msgs/msgs/Twist

ros2 pub -r 10 -t 6 /turtle1/cmd_vel geometry_msgs/msgs/Twist "Linear x,y,z" ( r is for hz rate 1s မှာ msgs ဘယ်နှစ်စောင် ပို့မလဲ? t is for time second)
